aha, NE]] || Minnesota\n|-\n|[[Big West Conference]] || [[2018 Cal State Fullerton Titans baseball team|Cal State Fullerton]] || Alex McKenna, {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=Cal Poly Mustangs|title=Cal Poly}}<ref name=\"Big West awards\">{{cite press release|url=http://www.bigwest.org/story.asp?STORY_ID=20616 |title=Big West Announces Baseball Honors |publisher=Big West Conference |date=May 30, 2018 |accessdate=June 7, 2018}}</ref>{{efn|group=cw|The Big West styles its Player of the Year award as \"Field Player of the Year\".}} || Colton Eastman, Cal State Fullerton<ref name=\"Big West awards\"/> || [[Rick Vanderhook]], Cal State Fullerton<ref name=\"Big West awards\"/> || ''No tournament, regular season champion earns auto bid'' || || Cal State Fullerton\n|-\n| [[Colonial Athletic Association]] || {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=Northeastern Huskies|title=Northeastern}} || Charlie McConnell, Northeastern<ref name=\"CAA awards\">{{cite press release|url=http://caasports.com/news/2018/5/22/mcconnell-rooney-headline-2018-all-caa-baseball-team.aspx |title=McConnell, Rooney Headline 2018 All-CAA Baseball Team |publisher=Colonial Athletic Association |date=May 22, 2018 |accessdate=June 7, 2018}}</ref> || John Rooney, {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=Hofstra Pride|title=Hofstra}}<ref name=\"CAA awards\"/> || [[Mike Glavine]], Northeastern<ref name=\"CAA awards\"/> || [[2018 Colonial Athletic Association Baseball Tournament]] || [[Eagle Field at Veterans Memorial Park]] \u2022 [[Harrisonburg, Virginia|Harrisonburg, VA]] || {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=UNC Wilmington Seahawks|title=UNC Willmington}}\n|-\n| [[Conference USA]] || {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=Southern Miss Golden Eagles|title=Southern Miss}} || Luke Reynolds, Southern Miss<ref name=\"C-USA awards\">{{cite press release|url=http://conferenceusa.com/news/2018/5/22/baseball-base-2018-awards-announced.aspx |title=BASE: 2018 Awards Announced |publisher=Conference USA |date=May 22, 2018 |accessdate=June 7, 2018}}</ref> || [[Nick Sandl