wac.org/ViewArticle.dbml?SPSID=632818&SPID=93274&DB_LANG=C&DB_OEM_ID=27400&ATCLID=211715719 |title=SWAC Announces 2018 Baseball Postseason Honors |publisher=Southwestern Athletic Conference |date=May 14, 2018 |accessdate=June 12, 2018}}</ref> || Aaron Solis, Texas Southern<ref name=\"SWAC awards\"/> || [[Jose Vazquez (baseball)|Jose Vazquez]], Alabama State<ref name=\"SWAC awards\"/> || [[2018 Southwestern Athletic Conference Baseball Tournament]] || [[Wesley Barrow Stadium]] \u2022 [[New Orleans|New Orleans, LA]] || Texas Southern\n|-\n| [[Summit League]] || {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=Oral Roberts Golden Eagles|title=Oral Roberts}} || Noah Cummings, Oral Roberts<ref name=\"Summit awards\">{{cite press release|url=http://thesummitleague.org/sports/bsb/2017-18/releases/20180521mjt2ag |title=Oral Roberts' Cummings, Ausua Named #SummitBSB Player and Pitcher of the Year |publisher=The Summit League |date=May 22, 2018 |accessdate=June 12, 2018}}</ref> || Miguel Ausua, Oral Roberts<ref name=\"Summit awards\"/> || [[Ryan Folmar]], Oral Roberts<ref name=\"Summit awards\"/> || [[2018 Summit League Baseball Tournament]] || [[J. L. Johnson Stadium]] \u2022 [[Tulsa, Oklahoma|Tulsa, OK]] || Oral Roberts\n|-\n| [[Sun Belt Conference]] || East - [[2018 Coastal Carolina Chanticleers baseball team|Coastal Carolina]]<br>West - [[2018 Louisiana Ragin' Cajuns baseball team|Louisiana]] || Joey Denison, {{CBSB link|year=2018|team=Troy Trojans|title=Troy}}<ref name=\"Sun Belt awards\">{{cite press release|url=http://sunbeltsports.org/news/2018/5/21/sun-belt-conference-announces-end-of-season-baseball-honors.aspx |title=Sun Belt Conference Announces End of Season Baseball Honors |publisher=Sun Belt Conference |date=May 21, 2018 |accessdate=June 11, 2018}}</ref> || Colten Schmidt, Louisiana<ref name=\"Sun Belt awards\"/> || [[Gary Gilmore (baseball)|Gary Gilmore]], Coastal Carolina<ref name=\"Sun Belt awards\"/> || [[2018 Sun Belt Conference Baseball Tournament]] || [[M. L. Tigue Moore Fiel